{"tid":1281033,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"《是你教我們和平遊行是沒用的》呢張圖係海外文宣必用！","createTime":"2019-07-03T07:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T01:47:13.000Z","uid":8244,"like":142,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"821b4faa0ee8f7d4a215889c33aee7dc4d7c2562","tid":1281033,"uid":8244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W0is8Ff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW0is8Ff.png&h=7f8f43a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張圖係來自BBC既一篇報導 （Hong Kong protests: What LegCo graffiti tells us）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-48836048?fbclid=IwAR3HO5vZaMcwLqRbJ6ozLgNtLBrO7X1jZ98k0T26oF9VOENd3_ykzI0kvJk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-48836048%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3HO5vZaMcwLqRbJ6ozLgNtLBrO7X1jZ98k0T26oF9VOENd3_ykzI0kvJk&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=68b4a204\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-48836048%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3HO5vZaMcwLqRbJ6ozLgNtLBrO7X1jZ98k0T26oF9VOENd3_ykzI0kvJk&h=40fa3a1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-48836048?fbclid=IwAR3HO5vZaMcwLqRbJ6ozLgNtLBrO7X1jZ98k0T26oF9VOENd3_ykzI0kvJk</a><br />\n<br />\n呢句野完全表達左抗爭者既迫不得而同埋當權者對和平集會既無視！"},{"pid":"bbb3e6d10da320784b1dae9d3f255d6342c3ae41","tid":1281033,"uid":8244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:14:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7c4c64707a471904ed6de9e61ab636ccb50eb76","tid":1281033,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:16:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c351bfe3930def6aabfac91f86b65d42b02b281f","tid":1281033,"uid":8244,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:17:10.000Z","msg":"呢張圖我見twitter 係好多討論"},{"pid":"6484b4f94bbd68b77f175429970daec637a6b180","tid":1281033,"uid":8244,"like":3,"dislike":0,"scor